{"tid":1017593,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"私修三國志11 需要附SIRE1.28d遊玩 大部份人物能力值參考313加埋美化","createTime":"2019-02-11T14:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T14:39:40.000Z","uid":212878,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0107ce1759553c89a93c851d8ef3bc60760f983c","tid":1017593,"uid":212878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:14:34.000Z","msg":"修改左三國志11 部份人物能力自己改左 例如夏侯敦 統率75 曹純統率78 張繡 武力82<br />\n捕縛+15% 傾國無視姓別 改名為謀斷 霸王改名為軍神<br />\n徐榮有疾馳 賈詡毒士=反計+虛實 司馬懿=謀斷+深謀=沮授+田豐 張遼=顏良+文醜 荀攸=妙計+百出 項羽 霸王=軍神+戰神+恫嚇<br />\n法正有謀斷<br />\n仲有將城既內政空地增加 同埋遠離海邊by遊俠網<br />\n五子良將<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/quZWD5n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FquZWD5n.jpg&h=345ac378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XeHk5LN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXeHk5LN.jpg&h=9dc1b1fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QyJHzFG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQyJHzFG.jpg&h=0bbfeb4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3gRs1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3gRs1c.jpg&h=8209ffd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aod4N1w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faod4N1w.jpg&h=c1a4c10e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美化部份頭像、新武器等 大部份都係遊俠網搵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Crq3jcK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCrq3jcK.jpg&h=6b75b8d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MiQuZfL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMiQuZfL.jpg&h=fd4d321b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新老年頭像<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2gFmBT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2gFmBT.jpg&h=efb9c901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三國志9有出現的人物、官方三國志11(CS)、官方13出既歷史武將 同埋我自己整既歷史武將等(除左11CS魅力我自己比)<br />\n官方三國志11(CS)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ir1RtaL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fir1RtaL.jpg&h=c84b7457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三國志9<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j4Dkmwd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4Dkmwd.jpg&h=687e74bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官方13出既歷史武將<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFH9eRL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFH9eRL.jpg&h=662c6aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我自己整既歷史武將<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxr9ZiM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxxr9ZiM.jpg&h=1b472af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炎王亂世MODE 景<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mT4GQsx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmT4GQsx.jpg&h=afbb8f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSAN11 sire 1.28d<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1ybinc1fqAxKYUCkYzLNMJibeP6kopfr8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1ybinc1fqAxKYUCkYzLNMJibeP6kopfr8&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1yVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=b8ce037a\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1ybinc1fqAxKYUCkYzLNMJibeP6kopfr8</a><br />\n原人物修改,新人物file,放入文件KOEI 覆蓋San11 Tc (請先保留備份整個file,因為有我打既save係入面同埋新人物)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1-cmAZ77dyIZWM4BOn1oCCZzNtX0gGgsZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1-cmAZ77dyIZWM4BOn1oCCZzNtX0gGgsZ&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1yVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=d25069f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1-cmAZ77dyIZWM4BOn1oCCZzNtX0gGgsZ</a><br />\n新武器圖 炎王亂世MODE 景有四季(因為好正 囉左來用) 將3個放入media 取代(請先保留備份整個file)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1chPcn1tK2bCRO15R-xIuosmc0Hgcgb-u\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1chPcn1tK2bCRO15R-xIuosmc0Hgcgb-u&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1yVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=27690a69\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1chPcn1tK2bCRO15R-xIuosmc0Hgcgb-u</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1B4loqzw3Ow1vE72Uis-qDoYOWFZcIFFO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1B4loqzw3Ow1vE72Uis-qDoYOWFZcIFFO&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1yVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=94f6f914\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1B4loqzw3Ow1vE72Uis-qDoYOWFZcIFFO</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=14kJP7lF5ePnKzq_pnMAy8uwYuKAWHJWY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D14kJP7lF5ePnKzq_pnMAy8uwYuKAWHJWY&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1yVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=cb96d04d\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=14kJP7lF5ePnKzq_pnMAy8uwYuKAWHJWY</a><br />\n新武器圖同埋老年頭像要用san11 editor 修改save001 <br />\n例如 新老年頭<br />\n打開左editor開啟入SAVE 按其他&gt;導入 搵我比你既San11 Tc 的SaveData&gt;SceCharData 開啟 之後保留隱藏屬性 其他取消<br />\n新武器一樣 不過係入SceItemData 保留屬性其他取消 (因為圖片只能換 不能多)<br />\n311 editor<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1LI66UPo-lmyO_E3oSvkG2kP78zP8h_dL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1LI66UPo-lmyO_E3oSvkG2kP78zP8h_dL&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1yVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=13fc150e\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1LI66UPo-lmyO_E3oSvkG2kP78zP8h_dL</a>"},{"pid":"52bc40afceb63eff151d67b6383b048e9acb8dc1","tid":1017593,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3c56e832161822a3af3fcc92843e362299e065","tid":1017593,"uid":51618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27be7ad18caf376523cdbba